metadata.name: Beginning
metadata.description:
Following the comprehension of his own beginning, human being tries to believe his existence; the existence in an independent position. Human being tries to stand on his own feet, to experience, creat definitions and rules to live a better life. 
But what is the real meaning of life? 

1. Standing and breathing
2. Leaving and going far beyond 
3. Staying and coming close 

Choose and take its responsibility! 

⦁Choreography: Hani
⦁Collection: Existential Art

(It must be noted that this work of art is unique and all of the objects are original)

∎Technical Specifications:
⦁Photography, photomontage
⦁Size: 6240 * 4160 pixel
⦁Resolution: 300 DPI
